*Zadnji* put smo se videli pre deset godina. (We last saw each other ten years ago.)

U *zadnjoj* godini života naučio sam mnogo. (In my last year of life I have learned a lot.)

*Zadnji* komad torte je bio najbolji. (The last piece of cake was the best.)

*Zadnjim* autobusom ću biti kod tebe za pola sata. (I will be with you in half an hour by the last bus.)

Mislio sam da je to *zadnji* put da odem. (I thought that was the last time I would go.)